OL,3,C#5.5bn lost to tax evasion could be
OL,4,C'vast underestimate' by HMRC, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe cross-party group of MPs has
OL,7,Fcalled on HMRC to establish a clear
OL,8,Fstrategy for tackling evasion and
OL,9,Fdeliberate non-compliance in a
OL,10,Fscathing report published on Wednesday.
OL,12,FHMRC estimated that tax-dodging cost
OL,13,FBritain #5.5 billion in 2022-2023, but
OL,14,Fhas acknowledged that this calculation
OL,15,Fwas uncertain, with the committee
OL,16,Fchairman warning that the "many
OL,17,Fbillions rightfully meant for the
OL,18,Fpublic purse could just be the tip of
OL,19,Fthe iceberg."
