OL,3,C#5.5bn lost to tax evasion could be
OL,4,C'vast underestimate' by HMRC, MPs warn
OL,6,FIn its report, the PAC said that
OL,7,Floopholes in the current system are
OL,8,Fmaking it easy for fraudulent
OL,9,Fbehaviour to go undetected.
OL,11,FVAT registrations processes, for
OL,12,Fexample, are "far too open to abuse,"
OL,13,Fand the authority is not exploring
OL,14,Foptions to tighten controls
OL,15,Fsufficiently, it warned.
