OL,3,C#5.5bn lost to tax evasion could be
OL,4,C'vast underestimate' by HMRC, MPs warn
OL,6,FHMRC does not routinely check
OL,7,Faddresses when businesses register for
OL,8,Fthe levy, but says it has confidence
OL,9,Fthat its "risk-based" assessments,
OL,10,Fcombined with due diligence rules for
OL,11,Fonline marketplaces are "working
OL,12,Fwell," it said.
OL,14,F"We are concerned that HMRC is not
OL,15,Fsufficiently curious about the true
OL,16,Fscale of tax evasion," the report said.
