OL,3,C#5.5bn lost to tax evasion could be
OL,4,C'vast underestimate' by HMRC, MPs warn
OL,6,FWhile the authority recognises that
OL,7,Ftransaction`based reporting would give
OL,8,Fit access to more data, it has also
OL,9,Fnot carried out any analysis to assess
OL,10,Fwhether this would be good value for
OL,11,Fmoney, according to the committee.
OL,13,FSignificant gaps remain in controls
OL,14,Fdesigned to prevent evasion, the
OL,15,Freport said. For example, overseas
OL,16,Ftraders can still falsely register as
OL,17,FUK sellers and companies due to the
OL,18,Flax checks in both HMRC and Companies
OL,19,FHouse registration processes, the MPs
OL,20,Fwarned.
