OL,3,C#5.5bn lost to tax evasion could be
OL,4,C'vast underestimate' by HMRC, MPs warn
OL,6,FHMRC and the Insolvency Service are
OL,7,Falso not tackling tax-dodgers or rogue
OL,8,Fdirectors sufficiently, according to
OL,9,Fthe PAC report.
OL,11,FOne particular issue is retailers that
OL,12,Fallow themselves to go insolvent then
OL,13,Fset up again under a new registration,
OL,14,Fso the same directors can carry on
OL,15,Ftrading.
OL,17,FHMRC has previously estimated the
OL,18,Fpractice, known as phoenixism,
OL,19,Faccounted for 15% of its tax debt
OL,20,Flosses in 2022-23, equivalent to more
OL,21,Fthan #500 million.
